Package asap.faceengine.viseme

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    VisemeBinding
    The VisemeBinding maps from visemes to FaceUnits.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DisneyVisemes
    The list of Disney Visemes, used by the SAPI5 TTS engines for lipsynch info
    FACSVisemeBinding
    Implementation that realizers visemes as FACS expressions
    IKPBonnVisemes
    The list of Visemes from [1], developed for the German BOSS phoneme set.
    MorphVisemeBinding
    Implementation that realizers visemes as morphs
    MorphVisemeDescription
    Describes a morph frame
    VisemeToFACSMapping
    given a viseme number, return the appropriate FACSConfiguration The mapping is read from a resource file.
    VisemeToMorphMapping
    given a viseme number, return the appropriate morph target name.
